## Non-Functional Requirements
 FrontEnd must use **React JS** with -tailwind andvite 
- Database must store:  
  - Users  
  - Games (with description, price, category, stock count)  
  - Orders   
  


---

## Technology Stack
- **Backend**: .NET Framework, C#, ADO.NET   
- **FrontEnd**: React JS, Tailwind
- all database tables schemes located in DataBaseScheme folder 
- **Authentication**: Cookie-based or JWT (depending on requirements)  

